SUMMARY:Empower Yourself: Conspiracy Theories VS Opportunity Theories
DESCRIPTION:Raleigh & Triangle Activities Meetup Group\nAh\, now here’s 
 a skill you need to stay safe and reach better futures from the current ch
 aotic collective reality! Every consciousness makes its own belief-based c
 hoices\, with some worldviews being dangerous and worth avoiding. So\, are
  you able to convert conspiracies into opportunities? No? Well don’t fee
 l bad\, it’s not a commonly understood skill\, but it will be. Join us t
 he Sunday March 8\, 2026 for a free liberating talk on how to let go colle
 ctive fears and re-align to your own soul path for the positive future tha
 t you need.\n\nWhat kind of opportunity can be made out of a conspiracy? I
  certainly don’t mean how to profit on people’s fears! “Awww darn\, 
 that’s what I was looking for!” Well\, that’s what conspiracy theori
 es offer\, by herding people into reactive groups that power negative soci
 eties to control human beings. “Oooh sounds scary\, isn’t that the mat
 rix that I’m trying to escape?” Yes\, and If you don’t like a realit
 y then stop going back into the beliefs that generate it. It’s easy when
  you notice your own steps. See the choices you made that got into a mess\
 , and choose your way out with new better principles.\n\nPeople need to se
 e that conspiracy thinking is the conspiracy! Whoever believes that enters
  that reality – unless you’re just safely studying it. Educate yoursel
 f. Long before you actually meet bad actors in dangerous situations\, you 
 must choose your expectations. Defensive humans can generate various survi
 val personalities including victims\, bullies\, rescuers\, and martyrs. Wi
 th negative imagination based on past traumas\, people can get stuck in fe
 ars that their fears will happen. Conspiracy\, false! Fear is the sensatio
 n of a false belief\, a non-solution\, that you must change because the Un
 iverse actually has so much love for you. Learn to master your mind’s ch
 oices and you will teleport to better realities naturally.\n\nTeleport? Ye
 s\, that’s what manifesting really is. You move around a multiverse of e
 ternal possibilities. The simultaneity of spacetime means all things are a
 vailable\, like books in a library. If you don’t like the section that y
 ou’re in\, then stop reading and move on. Your current reality is like a
  book or movie that you can just exchange. How? Not by fighting the other 
 people where you want to leave\; that’s a popular mistake. Everyone has 
 their own reasons to be there. Different visitors to the same reality figh
 t each other when they don’t know how to change their own beliefs. To le
 ave a place you don’t enjoy\, just notice where you are\, consult maps\,
  ask for help\, and change your own lifestyle.\n\nYou already teleport to 
 experience change\, just badly to stage bad luck and suffering. Your best 
 times are positive worlds\, your worst times are negative worlds\, and bot
 h are always available. This means you’ve been to heaven many times\, so
  the trick you want is to stay there. This is a TOTALLY different way to u
 nderstand life and manifesting. You never have to struggle to make goals h
 appen or stop bad events. Life gets better naturally if you can see and fo
 llow energy. Experiencing loss and grief is a misuse of the spacetime libr
 ary filing system\, causing fear\, hurt\, and anger. These emotions compou
 nd into deeper negative states like anxiety\, panic\, outrage\, depression
 \, guilt\, and worry. This human suffering is tragically unnecessary\, bec
 ause the Universe will give you everything you need to live happy ever aft
 er. Just learn what’s true for you to stay in good places.\n\nThe old fa
 lse paradigm says that when you have a good moment\, the hard work has jus
 t begun to defend it. Human beings are forever insecure\, violently compet
 ing over vanishing resources. The new true paradigm says a good moment is 
 a portal to forever\, a seed to grow with grateful celebration. Don’t be
 lieve it? Of course not yet\, that’s the point. You gotta re-educate you
 rself to leave the negative matrix. Discover that there’s actually a pos
 itive matrix\, which is how you create your own reality for endless love a
 nd happiness.\n\nFor this meetup\, have the courage to face your own cynic
 ism and fears. What do you feel is against you in life? Where do you feel 
 powerless and victimized? Would you like to know how life really wants to 
 work perfectly for you? After some check-ins to share and relate\, I’ll 
 outline the great choice between positive and negative belief systems\, an
 d how you alone decide the outcome of your own life experience. You’ll l
 earn empowering approaches to find and change old false beliefs\, and we
 ’ll conclude with a guided meditation to put to rest the negative ego an
 d welcome the true higher self.\n\nWelcome! Our Inner Selves Mastery spiri
 tual support group is free online every Sunday 11am-130pm EDT\, with the l
 ast 30 minutes for a guided meditation. If you can’t stay you can get th
 e recording. You can signup here for this meeting and visit www.signupISM.
 com for all events\, newsletter\, videos\, and more.\n\nBest wishes\,\nCar
 l Johann Schroeder\nInner Selves Mastery\nspiritual teaching and coaching\
 nquick-links at [www.signupISM.com](http://www.signupISM.com)
