SUMMARY:Yoga + Sound Bath or come for Sound Bath only
DESCRIPTION:Raleigh & Triangle Activities Meetup Group\n💫 Join us for a
 n evening of deep relaxation.\n\nPLEASE NOTE: There are two options for th
 is event. Yoga and Sound Bath or Sound Bath Only. Registration and ticket 
 purchase information in description.\n\nIn this integrative journey of sel
 f-care\, we’ll begin with gentle yoga and then move into a meditative he
 aling sound bath. Or you can come just for the meditative sound healing ex
 perience\, where you will be deeply immersed in transformative sounds and 
 vibrations. Crystal singing bowls tuned to each chakra\, the Chao gong\, K
 oshi chimes\, tuning forks and more will wash over your body bringing you 
 to a state of harmony. There is an array of essential oils you can choose 
 to use to add to your experience\, as well as plant-based snacks to enjoy.
 \n\nThis workshop will support you to relax your body\, calm your mind\, c
 lear stuck energy and activate your natural healing systems.\n\nPlease bri
 ng your yoga mat and water. You may also want to bring blocks and a strap 
 if you're doing yoga\, and for the sound bath a blanket\, pillow\, eye cov
 ering and anything else you need to feel comfortable. Limited extra props 
 will be available.\n\nYOGA + SOUND BATH SCHEDULE\n4:45pm - Registration op
 ens\n5:00pm - Gentle yoga\n5:50pm - Break / Sound Bath participants come i
 n\n6:00pm - Meditative Sound Bath\nCOST: $35 per person (note the payment 
 options at check out)\n\nSOUND BATH ONLY SCHEDULE\n5:50pm - Break / Sound 
 Bath participants come in\n6:00pm - Meditative Sound Bath\nCOST: $25.00 pe
 r person (note the payment options at check out)\n\nIn order that we may b
 egin on time\, please pre-register (don't worry\, if something comes up yo
 u will be given credit for any future Yoga+Soundbath event) and arrive at 
 least 5 minutes early. Walk-ins permitted as space allows. Cash and Venmo 
 only accepted at the door.\nLocation: Unity Holistic Wellness Center\, 512
 4 Departure Drive\, Raleigh\, NC 27616\n\nFor more information and to regi
 ster:\nhttps://www.staceypaige.com/service-page/yoga-sound-bath
